defs.name: LexerErrorKind
defs.value:
pub enum LexerErrorKind {
    ExpectedCommentInline,
    ExpectedCommentLine,
    ExpectedIdentOrKeyword,
    ExpectedTipIdent,
    ExpectedBoolLit,
    ExpectedNoneLit,
    ExpectedFloatLit,
    ExpectedIntLit,
    ExpectedStringStartDelim,
    ExpectedStringInner,
    ExpectedStringEndDelim,
    ExpectedCharStartDelim,
    ExpectedCharInner,
    ExpectedCharEndDelim,
    ExpectedDec,
    ExpectedBin,
    ExpectedOct,
    ExpectedHex,
    ExpectedExp,
    ExpectedDecOrExp,
    ExpectedOperator,
    ExpectedHash,
    ExpectedLeftParen,
    ExpectedRightParen,
    ExpectedNewline,
    ExpectedPunc,
    UnexpectedEof,
    NoMatch,
    CouldNotParseFloat,
    Eof,
}
